## Part 5: Tech Stack

- **Framework:** Next.js 14.2+ (App Router)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS 3.4+
- **Animation:** Framer Motion 11+
- **Language:** TypeScript 5.3+
- **Fonts:** Cormorant (serif display/headlines) + DM Sans (body)
- **Deployment:** Vercel
- **CRM Integration:** ActiveCampaign
- **Optional:** Supabase (lead store). Env: `SUPABASE_URL`, `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY`. See `lib/leads-store.ts`.
- **Supabase migrations:** Run via **Supabase CLI** only (not manual SQL or dashboard). From repo root: `supabase link` (one-time, then `supabase db push` to apply `supabase/migrations/*.sql`).
- **Data:** JSON files in `/data` directory (single source of truth)

