## Part 10: Component Patterns

### Buttons (Luxury Black/White Standard)

**CTA color decision:** Primary CTAs (header "Book Trial," key actions) use black/white only. Sunset Cliff is for hover states and accents only — not primary button fill. No orange/red primary buttons.

**Hero CTA on dark:** When the primary CTA sits on a dark hero or gradient (e.g. from-black/75), use a solid background (e.g. bg-white text-black or bg-black text-white) so contrast meets WCAG 7:1. Do not use text-only (e.g. text-black with no bg) on dark backgrounds.

```tsx
// Primary CTA (Book Trial, Register)
<button className="
  inline-flex items-center justify-center
  bg-black text-white
  font-sans text-sm font-medium
  tracking-[2.5px] uppercase
  min-h-[48px] px-10 py-4
  rounded-[2px]
  transition-all duration-300 ease-out
  hover:bg-gray-800 hover:-translate-y-0.5
  focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-black/30 focus:ring-offset-2
">
  Book Trial
</button>

// Secondary (Learn More, Explore)
<button className="
  inline-flex items-center justify-center
  bg-transparent text-black
  border border-black/20
  font-sans text-sm font-medium
  tracking-[2.5px] uppercase
  min-h-[48px] px-10 py-4
  rounded-[2px]
  transition-all duration-300 ease-out
  hover:border-black hover:-translate-y-0.5
  focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-black/30 focus:ring-offset-2
">
  Learn More
</button>
```

### Cards
```tsx
<div className="
  bg-white
  border border-black/6
  transition-all duration-500 ease-out
  shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.02),0_2px_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.02),0_4px_8px_rgba(0,0,0,0.02)]
  hover:border-black/10 hover:-translate-y-1
  hover:shadow-[0_4px_8px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03),0_8px_16px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03),0_16px_32px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)]
">
  {/* Card content */}
</div>
```

### Images
- Use `next/image` only; `alt` and `sizes` are required. Use `priority` only for the LCP/hero image(s).
```tsx
import Image from 'next/image'

<Image
  src="/images/example.webp"
  alt="Descriptive alt text under 125 characters"
  width={1200}
  height={800}
  loading="lazy"
  quality={90}
  className="object-cover w-full h-full"
  sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 1200px) 50vw, 33vw"
/>

// For hero/above-fold images, add priority
<Image ... priority />
```

**Logo usage:** Header and Footer use local `/logos/LBTAblktext.png` (Footer inverts on dark). PartnershipSection uses `/logos/*` with descriptive alt. No external logo URLs; keep assets in `public/logos/`.

**Footer and dark sections:** On bg-brand-deep-water (or any dark section), use text-white/50 or higher for tagline and secondary text to meet WCAG 7:1 contrast. Avoid text-white/40 or text-white/25 for body or tagline.

**Section accents:** Use HorizonDivider or the `.section-horizon` utility under key section headings per Brand Guide; pull quotes use `.section-quote` (gradient left edge).

